              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
  A <fr:link href="/schm-V16H/" title="Locally distributed space" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-V16H/" display-uri="schm-V16H" type="local">locally distributed space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(X,\mathcal {O}_{X})]]></fr:tex> is a <html:em>scheme</html:em>, if for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  X]]></fr:tex> there is an open neighbourhood <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[U]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x]]></fr:tex>, such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(U,\mathcal {O}_{X}|_U)]]></fr:tex> is an <fr:link href="/schm-IFX1/" title="Affine scheme" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-IFX1/" display-uri="schm-IFX1" type="local">affine scheme</fr:link>. The full subcategory of schemes will be denoted as <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {Sch}_{\mathbb {D}}]]></fr:tex>.
